      remember = [SharedLinkVerif]
      width = min(750px, 100%)
      height = min(150px)
      takesUpFullRow = true
      //foldToggleState = shown
      excludeFromShareLink = false
      examples
        ⓘ Click the button above to change how the tags are separated.\n\nⓘ Place #tag# in the description, and here place the tags you want. The word #tag# in the description will be replaced by the words/tags that are here.

